{
  "stem": "8212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very dour people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are some exceptions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not too friendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose so, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because lots of them were like Germany and-- I mean, non-Jewish Swiss.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't mind at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And lots of people were actually sent back, especially the ones that tried to cross the border directly from Austria and Germany, earlier.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lots of them were sent back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That my what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think my mother was absolutely incredible, because she did most of everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, who used to be working and not being home, did some things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my mother is the woman-- the women that really held it all together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because she made sure that we had a warm clothes and a place to sleep and food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember, even in Lyon, there was very little food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to queue up in front of stores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They said, today, this store has eggs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So everybody stood for hours to get a couple of eggs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Today, this store has sardines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my sister, my mother, and I would just stand in front of those stores for hours to get a box of sardines and to get this or that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then I remember there was a marvelous chocolate store in Lyon where they, every once in a while, sold marvelous chocolates.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, we queued up there and we bought the chocolates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother just sold them or exchanged them for food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We never ate those marvelous chocolates because, for us, it was like money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I will always remember there we get those wonderful chocolates and we couldn't eat them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So all these things happened during Lyon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were in your late teens at this point.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think the resistance was later.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
